dd83f377-95be-410c-9b47-fc79c241c5bd.title: King Bolren
dd83f377-95be-410c-9b47-fc79c241c5bd.text:
Well hello stranger. My name's Bolren, I'm the king of
the tree gnomes.

0c53dbaa-acef-497c-800a-d572e6ea88ca.title: King Bolren
0c53dbaa-acef-497c-800a-d572e6ea88ca.text:
I'm surprised you made it in, maybe I made the maze
too easy.

c70fac86-1552-4976-ab03-c6480455fbcb.title: King Bolren
c70fac86-1552-4976-ab03-c6480455fbcb.text:
I'm afraid I have more serious concerns at the
moment. Very serious.

options.text: I'll leave you to it then.

b179f528-acea-4998-8f79-0464bee782d1.title: <player>
b179f528-acea-4998-8f79-0464bee782d1.text: I'll leave you to it then.

f0bec7fb-a36d-4a72-a506-ca90ddb1570c.title: King Bolren
f0bec7fb-a36d-4a72-a506-ca90ddb1570c.text:
The truth is my people are in grave danger. We have
always been protected by the Spirit Tree. No creature
of dark can harm us while its three orbs are in place.

b1f6571d-81ad-40e0-b5e2-86a064b33b7a.title: King Bolren
b1f6571d-81ad-40e0-b5e2-86a064b33b7a.text:
We are not a violent race, but we fight when we must.
Many gnomes have fallen battling the dark forces of
Khazard to the North.

ea977e3f-223f-4e13-9cb4-2db6138f424d.title: King Bolren
ea977e3f-223f-4e13-9cb4-2db6138f424d.text:
We became desperate, so we took one orb of protection
to the battlefield. It was a foolish move.

95a2c614-0e7b-4828-85f4-d97cc4fc8a93.title: King Bolren
95a2c614-0e7b-4828-85f4-d97cc4fc8a93.text:
Khazard troops seized the orb. Now we are completely
defenceless.

5ec0257c-09fa-413b-9f34-451cafbc84d9.title: King Bolren
5ec0257c-09fa-413b-9f34-451cafbc84d9.text:
You would be a huge benefit on the battlefield. If you
would go there and try to retrieve the orb, my people
and I will be forever grateful.

3b8754fb-d715-4acb-8fc8-3045f401a96e.title: <player>
3b8754fb-d715-4acb-8fc8-3045f401a96e.text: I'm sorry but I won't be involved.

d67e2b49-888b-464b-aa81-b9f9a859a2ae.text:
Before starting this quest, be aware that your combat level is lower
than the recommended level of 45.

fbfce729-0de7-46e7-aae8-a8bba4748ffc.title: <player>
fbfce729-0de7-46e7-aae8-a8bba4748ffc.text: I would be glad to help.

fd31dba7-563a-4630-951e-9bf66cac1bb1.title: King Bolren
fd31dba7-563a-4630-951e-9bf66cac1bb1.text:
Thank you. The battlefield is to the north of the maze.
Commander Montai will inform you of their current
situation.

be3abbf6-9043-4dc5-b18b-822d577a1a53.title: King Bolren
be3abbf6-9043-4dc5-b18b-822d577a1a53.text: That is if he's still alive.

ac5f65db-d905-451b-afb9-01b773bb4a8f.title: King Bolren
ac5f65db-d905-451b-afb9-01b773bb4a8f.text:
My assistant shall guide you out. Good luck friend, try
your best to return the orb.

e32fc27b-4081-4abb-ad76-4a70ece8f817.text: Elkoy guides you out of the maze.

98a5f224-4300-4a7c-9dba-1c5e74695df2.title: Note
98a5f224-4300-4a7c-9dba-1c5e74695df2.text:
starts tree gnome village quest (TGV)
also you get teleported to Elkoy in the northwestern part of the maze

a98108da-0304-4281-a122-729cffae4bda.title: Elkoy
a98108da-0304-4281-a122-729cffae4bda.text:
We're out of the maze now. Please hurry, we must
have the orb if we are to survive.

24445cd7-a056-4c46-acdd-c384c14c4544.title: King Bolren
24445cd7-a056-4c46-acdd-c384c14c4544.text:
Hello traveller, we must retrieve the orb. It's being held
by Khazard troops north of here.

4e0e1048-864c-4c4a-b2df-5c259111b629.title: King Bolren
4e0e1048-864c-4c4a-b2df-5c259111b629.text:
The orb is being held at the battlefield north of the
maze.

753a1cdc-2716-452e-a3b1-a75f0a3a233e.title: King Bolren
753a1cdc-2716-452e-a3b1-a75f0a3a233e.text: Please, we must have the orb if we are to survive.

2bbd6cd2-9778-4091-899d-69ae7ab97677.title: King Bolren
2bbd6cd2-9778-4091-899d-69ae7ab97677.text: Oh my... The misery, the horror!

91a12fe3-d126-4dad-9cab-d6d9bf99cc4d.title: King Bolren
91a12fe3-d126-4dad-9cab-d6d9bf99cc4d.text: Thank you traveller, but it's too late. We're all doomed.

943813ee-6249-48d5-990a-b316c03b0fa5.title: King Bolren
943813ee-6249-48d5-990a-b316c03b0fa5.text:
They came in the night. I don't know how many, but
enough.

f059e00c-cee1-48f1-a642-f8a7bd20741e.title: King Bolren
f059e00c-cee1-48f1-a642-f8a7bd20741e.text:
Khazard troops. They slaughtered anyone who got in
their way. Women, children, my wife.

03f2d04a-8716-4555-b43b-b1e45d66ac7a.title: King Bolren
03f2d04a-8716-4555-b43b-b1e45d66ac7a.text: They took the other orbs, now we are defenceless.

68782f87-d1db-4a2d-a60a-e9010c6c0a2f.title: King Bolren
68782f87-d1db-4a2d-a60a-e9010c6c0a2f.text:
They headed north of the stronghold. A warlord carries
the orbs.

options.text: I will find the warlord and bring back the orbs.
I'm sorry but I can't help.

cc4fb57c-ce3e-47bc-829d-240494e674a6.title: <player>
cc4fb57c-ce3e-47bc-829d-240494e674a6.text: I'm sorry but I can't help.

707c47e4-ef24-4c5b-9ec7-54d3faac7135.title: King Bolren
707c47e4-ef24-4c5b-9ec7-54d3faac7135.text: I understand, this isn't your battle.

d838c93f-8b0b-40b8-8abf-16504ebce68d.title: <player>
d838c93f-8b0b-40b8-8abf-16504ebce68d.text: I will find the warlord and bring back the orbs.

96f5b517-cea2-4124-a66f-c395be53dbaf.title: King Bolren
96f5b517-cea2-4124-a66f-c395be53dbaf.text:
You are brave, but this task will be tough even for you.
I wish you the best of luck. Once again you are our
only hope.

af0e06e7-c3fb-46b7-af18-cd45958c2cc5.title: King Bolren
af0e06e7-c3fb-46b7-af18-cd45958c2cc5.text:
I will safeguard this orb and pray for your safe return.
My assistant will guide you out.

60cce1f7-dee7-4be4-8ee2-75dc422c8ffa.text: Elkoy guides you out of the maze.

4bf709ff-6454-4397-8e34-c7a5c84bfe19.text: you need to have the Orb of Protection with you.

025dd5cc-7eff-48f8-a899-080df1d9e1d6.title: Note
025dd5cc-7eff-48f8-a899-080df1d9e1d6.text:
take orb of protection
set quest to find warlord

60fe322e-26fd-42fa-8f87-c6d40174e7b0.title: King Bolren
60fe322e-26fd-42fa-8f87-c6d40174e7b0.text:
The orbs are gone, taken north of the battlefield by a
Khazard warlord. We're all doomed.

8b04ff0e-fef9-4dac-9a90-c61182a9c13e.title: King Bolren
8b04ff0e-fef9-4dac-9a90-c61182a9c13e.text: You made it back! Do you have the orbs?

b417401d-59b7-44d2-8630-7cda3cd95e83.title: King Bolren
b417401d-59b7-44d2-8630-7cda3cd95e83.text: Please, we must have the orbs if we are to survive.

acc9a721-9cd9-45d5-943c-edfdf9d4fa52.title: King Bolren
acc9a721-9cd9-45d5-943c-edfdf9d4fa52.text:
Hooray, you're amazing. I didn't think it was possible
but you've saved us.

1ed369e7-af40-4b60-9733-0d5d308f8a3f.title: King Bolren
1ed369e7-af40-4b60-9733-0d5d308f8a3f.text:
Once the orbs are replaced we will be safe once more.
We must begin the ceremony immediately.

bf6e674a-c9ec-4427-8d03-b1b913229678.title: King Bolren
bf6e674a-c9ec-4427-8d03-b1b913229678.text:
The spirit tree has looked over us for centuries. Now
we must pay our respects.

ad519356-0279-4445-bbfe-6f051d76c512.text:
The gnomes begin to chant. Meanwhile, King Bolren holds the orbs
of protection out in front of him.

f8b9950c-608a-40a7-8fcf-f657e29c5a77.text:
The orbs of protection come to rest gently in the branches of the
ancient spirit tree.

87336b1c-2150-430d-ba09-eb25b1163499.title: King Bolren
87336b1c-2150-430d-ba09-eb25b1163499.text:
Now at last my people are safe once more. We can live
in peace again.

a32c29a3-ea37-4612-8b11-e818bfe2714a.title: King Bolren
a32c29a3-ea37-4612-8b11-e818bfe2714a.text:
Please, for your efforts take this amulet. It's made
from the same sacred stone as the orbs of protection. It
will help keep you safe on your journeys.

ec1c6b0c-3b61-4659-a927-a0aff0916f3c.title: King Bolren
ec1c6b0c-3b61-4659-a927-a0aff0916f3c.text:
The tree has many other powers, some of which I
cannot reveal. As a friend of the gnome people, I can
now allow you to use the tree's magic to teleport to
other trees grown from related seeds.

9a570a7b-d3d1-4c19-be39-4fa23ed5d0fa.title: Quest Complete
9a570a7b-d3d1-4c19-be39-4fa23ed5d0fa.text:
2 QUEST POINTS
11,450 ATTACK XP
SPIRIT TREE ACCESS
A GNOME AMULET

a647ddca-3ab0-4c7c-88be-897ac0e82f2e.title: King Bolren
a647ddca-3ab0-4c7c-88be-897ac0e82f2e.text: Hello there. It's good to see you again.

534d657c-4935-4e82-b663-dd21606da849.title: King Bolren
534d657c-4935-4e82-b663-dd21606da849.text:
Those Khazard troops continue to be a menace, but
things are much better now. All thanks to you, of
course.

086a7f7d-b0c2-496b-afea-cb1c63d64d27.text:
You do not meet all of the requirements to start
The Path of Glouphrie quest.

999d0efc-9137-4312-a00a-af88d1f74d82.title: Note
999d0efc-9137-4312-a00a-af88d1f74d82.text:
Path of Glouphrie requirements
Eyes of Glouphrie
Tree Gnome Village
Waterfall Quest

Recommend 60 cmb lvl

9e763a0d-49a9-444e-ab4f-1ec681712d9a.text:
Before starting this quest, be aware that your combat level is lower
than the recommended level of 60.
